tafsir[44]{c,v,t}:
  70,1,"Gooto e sirkoo…ďe …ďen toranike e hoore mun e yim…ďe mun …ďen lette, himo jalkita, sikkugol lette …óen wa…óaatah. Hara …óum wa…óay √Ďalnde Darngal."
  70,2,"Wonannde yeddu…ďe Allah …ďen, alah du√Īanoowo …ďe …óee lette."
  70,3,"Ko immorde ka Allha, Jom toowal e darja, e …ďure e neemaaji."
  70,4,"Malaa'ika'en wonndude e Jibriilu hino e ∆īawa e …óin darjaaji √Ďalnde Darngal, juutungal, e…ď…ďirtengal duu…ďi ujune cappan…óe jowi."
  70,5,"Mu√Ī√Īo tun, yo Nulaa…óo, mu√Īal ngal jillah …óen∆īagol maa wullitagol."
  70,6,"Kam…ďe hi…ďe reeni …óee lette ko wo…ó…óii…óe tultooje."
  70,7,"Menen le Me…óen reeni …óe ko …ďadii…óe, yanay…óe feere mun alaa."
  70,8,"√Ďalnde kammu ngun wa'oyta wano sila maa kaŇčŇče taayinaa…óum."
  70,9,"Pelle …óen kadi wa'oya wano hottollo goobaako saraako."
  70,10,"Ka …ďadondiraa…óo lamdotaako fii musi…ó…óo mun, tawde haray mo kala hino sokliri hoore mun."
  70,11,"Kala ma…ď…ďe yi'ay …ďadondiraa…óo mun on ka suu…óaaki. Wondude e …óum fof gooto lamndotaako fii oya hakkee ko annde. Hanndu…óo e Yiite ngen yeloo jonnugol …ďi…ó…ďe makko …ďen fii sottorgol mo lette …óen."
  70,12,"O sottora gennda makko e neene gooto makko on."
  70,13,"o sottora kadi gorol makko …ďa…óii…ďe mo, …ďen …ďannitaynoo …ďe mo si sattii."
  70,14,"O sottora kadi kala yim…ďe e jinna ekw ko woni kon ka leydi, refti o jonnira …óum fii sottoragol, da…ónda hoore makko lette Yiite ngen."
  70,15,"∆äum gasirtaa wano bon…óo on yelori. Yiite laakara ngen ko uuyaynge hu…ď…ďa."
  70,16,"∆Āoltaynge wippita guri hoore; hakkee ko nge wuli e konge hu…ď…ďi."
  70,17,"Hinge nodda on …óuurnii…óo goonga, o hucciti o salii gom…óinnde mbo o ronki gollude."
  70,18,"O moo…ďi jawle, o mari ndi fii wata o nafqu ndi e laawol Allah."
  70,19,"Pellet, ne…ó…óo on tagaama ko o tii…óu…óo reer…óugol."
  70,20,"Si lorra nawnaare maa baasal memii mo, tawaa ko o fan…óu…óo mu√Īal."
  70,21,"Si ko he…ďii mbo ko weltinta hono amo e ngalu he…ďii mo, o wona tii…óu…óo salorgol …óum e fii laawol Allah ngol."
  70,22,"Si wanaa juuloo…ďe …ďen, …ďen …óon hino hisi e …óin jikkuuji Ňči√Īaa…ói."
  70,23,"∆Āen taw…ďe ko duumii…ďe e juulde ma…ď…ďe nden, …ďe welsindotaako e mayre, …ďe tottira nde e waqtu mayre happaa…óo on."
  70,24,"E …ďen taw…ďe hino e jawle ma…ď…ďe …óen ge…ďal dottangal farlangal."
  70,25,"Ge…ďal nagl …ďe ittanta torotoo…óo …ďe e baaso mo torortaako."
  70,26,"E …ďen goooginany…ďe √Ďalaande Darngal nden. √Ďalnde Allah yo…ďitoyta kala e ko o haanndi kon."
  70,27,"E …ďen taw…ďe hi…ďe huli lette Joomi ma…ď…ďe …óen, e hoore ko …ďe ardini e golle mo∆ī∆īe kon fow."
  70,28,"Pellet, lette Joomi ma…ď…ďe …óen, ko hul…ďinii…óe …óe haqqil…óo haanaa hoolaade da…óugol."
  70,29,"E …ďen taw…ďe hino reenir…ďe farjuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin : surragol wo…ó…óitoo e pankare."
  70,30,"Si wanaa e rew…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen maa e hor…ďe ko …ďe jeyi kon, …ďe feletaake …óon on fii dakmitorgol …ďen mbalndi e tanaa mun."
  70,31,"Kala non …óa…ď…ďu…óo ka dakmitora hara wanaa e …ďen rew…ďe e hor…ďe jantaa…ďe, haray ko …ďen woi yawtu…ďe keeri Allah …óin."
  70,32,"E …ďen taw…ďe si …ďe hoolnaama e jawle e gunndoo ekw, e aynitoo…ďe ahadiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin e yim…ďe …ďen kulol wata hoolaare bonu …ďe firtatah aadi."
  70,33,"E …ďen taw…ďe ko √Īii…ďir…ďe e seedeeji ma…ď…ďe …óin no haaniri, tawata jeydal maa e ngayngu battintaa e mun."
  70,34,"E …ďen taw…ďe hi…ďe reenorii e julde ma…ď…ďe nden, tottirgol nden e waqtu mayre, wonndude e laa…ďal e dee∆īere, hara huunde sokoliŇčtaa …ďe e mayre."
  70,35,"∆Āen siforaa…ďe …óin sifaaji, …ďe teddiniroyte e Aljannaaji, neemaaji √Īii…ďu…ói, e ndaaroygol Yeeso Allah Teddungo ngon."
  70,36,"E ko nanngi sirkoo…ďe jeyaa…ďe e yim…ďe maa …ďen, an Nulaa…óo, hi…ďe he√Īora fennugol ma?"
  70,37,"Hi…ďe huu…ďitir-maa ka √Īaamo e ka nano, ko…ďe dentoy-dentoy."
  70,38,"Hara gooto kala e ma…ď…ďe tam∆īini nde Allah naadoyta mo Aljanna neemaaji, ka o neeminorta neemaaji duumii…ói, e hoore ko o heddii e keeferaaku mum?"
  70,39,"Wanaa no …ďe sikkiri non ! Men tagiri…ďe e ko …ďe anndi fii mun, woni ndihal hoykal, …ďe lohiri non kam…ďe kadi, tawde …ďe waawah nafude ko'e ma…ď…ďe wanah fii lorra. Ko honno non …ďe townitorta?"
  70,40,"Alla woondiri Hoore Makko ko Kanko woni jom Funnaangeeji e Hirnaangeeji naange e lewru e denndaangal koode wonde ko O kattan…óo."
  70,41,"Me…óen hattani wattirgol …ďe wo…ó…ďe goo, …óoftotoo…ďe Allah, Men halka fii ma…ď…ďe kam…ďe. Men siforaa ronkoo…ďe gaynude fii ma…ď…ďe, wattitira …ďe wo…ó…ďe goo si Men faandanike …óum."
  70,42,"Accu…ďe yo Nulaa…óo, …ďe jumpa e meere e majjere ko woni e mun, …ďe fija e nguurndam ma…ď…ďe aduna …óam haa …ďe hawroya e √Ďalaande Darngal nde …ďe kammbiranaa nden ka Alqur'aana."
  70,43,"√Ďalnde …ďe yaltirorta e gaburuuji …óin he√Īaare, wa si tawii hara ko kaa∆īe sanamu …ďe adandirta."
  70,44,"Hara gite ma…ď…ďe no heli, koyeera no suddi …ďe. Ko nden woni √Īalaande nde …ďe kammbirananoo nden e aduna, nde …ďe ittaanoo yiila e mun."
